{"tid":2112512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民黨林瑞華戰飲食界撼張宇人","createTime":"2020-07-17T11:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T12:03:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8385e5e730cda9361db849834be453f62cf35a9e","tid":2112512,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/PGG4V5XRSOAJFU5ASF4OK774TE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FPGG4V5XRSOAJFU5ASF4OK774TE%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=742a1674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FPGG4V5XRSOAJFU5ASF4OK774TE%2F&h=0128534b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/PGG4V5XRSOAJFU5ASF4OK774TE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公民黨林瑞華戰飲食界撼張宇人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x0u2LL9zHHaRPwSVmpOKendHnug=/680x564/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XOJGBXMVC76MEZTUCOYA3TNGMY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx0u2LL9zHHaRPwSVmpOKendHnug%3D%2F680x564%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXOJGBXMVC76MEZTUCOYA3TNGMY.gif&h=5ee0f752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n616牛肉火鍋專門店東主林瑞華昨在其餐廳宣佈出選。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派銳意在9月立法會選舉奪得「35+」，以重掌議會話語權，其中在功能組別至少要取得12席，才能達至議會過半數。今年初加入公民黨、為「大狀黨」內唯一有商界背景的火鍋店東主林瑞華，昨日宣佈以「開創時勢、突破限制」為競選口號參選飲食界立法會選舉，力撼連任四屆的自由黨主席張宇人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：戴耀廷「爭取休息」：靠選民自主配票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑斥張「唔化」<br />\n<br />\n被民主派視為最有機會搶灘的飲食界功能組別，今屆選民人數激增至7,965名，較上屆選民多出2,422名。若按照上屆數票結果計算，現任張宇人獲2,438票，如林瑞華能獲得今屆新增選民支持，民主派則有望能在飲食界別攻下一席。<br />\n<br />\n循飲食界出戰的中小企食。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨主席梁家傑指張宇人應。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否簽署確認書？梁家傑稱，公民黨。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今天撐場的名人梁芷珊直指，香港從未經歷現今困局，多間飲食店或面臨結業危機，指張宇人作為飲食界代表卻不作為，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d8479234d9da4bbc60b053f90306930bf8111598","tid":2112512,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"至於會否簽署確認書？梁家傑稱，公民黨現階段不會簽署，但<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">會跟隨本土派與泛民磋商後的決定為主，實行「齊上齊落」。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6833f4fe359008fc251c6843c22d66f0ddd6a1dc","tid":2112512,"uid":2501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"公 民 黨"},{"pid":"1620cdbcb69742d87f13516cb950122c6096927f","tid":2112512,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"公民黨到宜家個包袱都仲喺度<br />\n太鍚身"},{"pid":"e57925490708b3050f8f26d2b2faf4c41cb51882","tid":2112512,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"至於會否簽署確認書？梁家傑稱，公民黨現階段不會簽署，但<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">會跟隨本土派與泛民磋商後的決定為主，實行「齊上齊落」。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497c0e43704501a1e57afd74aab6510fef7ea63b","tid":2112512,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"09a48a2761eda1be652cbb8e331589d167475924","tid":2112512,"uid":173814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1620cdbcb69742d87f13516cb950122c6096927f","tid":2112512,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"r